dialogue.introduction: Hi, I'm Yuudachi, a Shiratsuyu-class destroyer. Nice to meet you!
dialogue.library_intro: I'm Yuudachi, the fourth ship of the Shiratsuyu class. I worked sort of hardish during the Third Battle of the Solomons didn't I? By the way, why am I so scared by the term "Ironbottom Sound?"
dialogue.secretary1: Did you, like, call? What is it?
dialogue.secretary2: What is it that you need, Admiral?
dialogue.secretary3: Hmm? What is it? Some kind of new game?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Err... Am I, like, neglected? Am I like, still insufficient?! Then I'll have to train more!
dialogue.secretarymarried: If it's for the Admiral's sake, I can like, get so much stronger.
dialogue.wedding: Admiral, your face looks reddish. Why? Love consultation? Person I like? Eh, no way, what should I do~?
dialogue.show_players_score: Seems a telegramish thing has arrived?
dialogue.equipment2: So I'm a newish version now?
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: I'm, like, going to have a nice lie-down.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new comrade has, like, just arrived.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: Seems like, the fleet came back?
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Sorry to have kept you waiting!
dialogue.battle_start: Now, let's have the most amazing party.
dialogue.attack: I wonder which ship I should start with?
dialogue.night_battle: Hmm... should we do a littlish bit more?
dialogue.mvp: I worked pretty hard? Admiral, praise me! Praise me!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Oh, you idiot... I, like, can't fight on like this-
dialogue.new_year_2015: Looks like its the new year! Looks like Yuudachi will be wearing her best clothes! Looks like...I can fight in these clothes!
dialogue.valentines_day_2015: Um, this chocolate-ish thing's for you. I did my bestest making it!
dialogue.white_day_2015: What is this package, Admiral? Smells nice~ It's cookies-poi! Perhaps these are handmade-poi?
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: It's an impoitant day! We should celebrate an amazing party on such day!
dialogue.early_summer_2015: Seems like it's getting hotter bit by bit. I guess summer's coming around again, poi!
dialogue.midsummer_2015: It may be my imagination, but this armour is, like, too thin. Poi...
dialogue.fall_2015: Autumns like, makes my tummy growl. Is the food ready yet? food～♪ food～♪
dialogue.fall_event_2015: If it's night battle I want you to bring me along-poi! I'm itching to fight-poi! Poi!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Mmm... the cake is so sweet and delicious poi! Umm...but if I eat too much, my displacement may exceed limitations poi. Po~i...
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: This year has already ended-poi. Somehow it came fast-poi. Yuudachi will also do her best next year-poi!
dialogue.setsubun_2016: This beans, and ish throw at full power! Ei! Ei! Eeei! Woah!
